nt|^b@2^z@3|cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|In general, in 3rd. seat you should be very aggressive when preempting. Open Weak-Twos with a 5-card suit when you have a singleton or void. And when not vul (especially against vul opponents) preempt 1 higher than you might otherwise.|
